OL,4,CLiverpool man trapped in Afghanistan
OL,5,Cpleads for help
OL,6, A British citizen who is stranded in
OL,7, Afghanistan after travelling to the
OL,8, country to help his family flee is
OL,9, pleading with the government for help.
OL,11,FThe taxi driver, who the BBC is calling
OL,12,FAhmed to protect his identity, flew
OL,13,Ffrom Liverpool as the Taliban seized
OL,14,Fcontrol of the country.
OL,16,FHe is currently in hiding with his wife
OL,17,Fand children after fleeing from the
OL,18,FAfghan capital Kabul.
OL,20,FAhmed told BBC North West Tonight that
OL,21,Fpeople "are desperate to leave".
